{"tid":1044954,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"從淘寶看見大灣區的未來","createTime":"2019-03-03T09:17:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T04:23:53.000Z","uid":222592,"like":4,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"17a54c2167eecc712569e47a82d4cbd366b2cb65","tid":1044954,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟之前從淘寶網上買野，<br />\n買十幾條黑鈦鏡面不銹鋼條，<br />\n其實都無他主要係係貪夠平，手工又唔差<br />\n（題外話依家香港9成建材都係大陸做，無論什麼什麼外國牌子都一撚樣）<br />\n<br />\n因為急用所以收貨地址選用順豐倉，想用埋順豐轉運，夠快，我屌佢老母送左成個星期都送唔到黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咪睇下咩事囉，原來件貨個單號咩撚野爛撚左，又比左個新單號黎。好我等！<br />\n<br />\n幾日後我一查，哇我屌！！！送左去西安（原收貨地點係廣東），仲要比人簽收埋，咁我緊係老西都唔比錢，要退貨， 點撚知個賣家拖拖拖，唔想退。<br />\n<br />\n到今日，要求第三方淘寶客服處理，客服條友岩岩打黎（廣東話），講左一堆野，但比我感覺跟本係冇心處理件事，只想盡快close file，又咩送你紅包又成，又一係叫我自己退貨退款，你醒我都唔傻，9秒9張所有同佢對話記錄打哂上去協商歷史到，點撚知佢一野DEL左，岩岩仲收到個咁既信息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/170948_e88418f672391dc38f36c224eb9c6355.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F170948_e88418f672391dc38f36c224eb9c6355.png&h=6e2c4216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n賣野嗰個出左貨就唔撚理，平台做野又是是但但。<br />\n呢次就網購姐，下次係醫療呢，再下次係公共建設問題呢？ <br />\n<br />\n咁既料子搞大灣區？算吧啦 <br />\n<br />\n最後利申：無錢移民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dde68759ebf6a2209b37b7340ea7d661f199a69","tid":1044954,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a01ac41c7247f7171cf0e66994740c27a498b1","tid":1044954,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fe68ee3e20b20919d046e8f4ac8aec8dae7df0","tid":1044954,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfff5f578a1180187483426b6a7a4c6fa1ff356","tid":1044954,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcfdbe912dc355efbcf788da7920ef7f776b3d6","tid":1044954,"uid":222592,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:25:03.000Z","ms